name: Where Am I...
description:
What a year this has been, I woke up into the meta asking myself 
where am i...what is this...until I became a part of this beautiful madness
of creativity.

I realized the power & beauty of darkness grew from art to artists and built amazing friendships. From meeting wonderful collectors to being consumed into collecting,
I found myself with almost 200 NFTs in my personal collection as the year ended.

I have been awakened yet again into another year this time better, stronger, with a Legion of Hunters & an amazing community.

Sending a gift to all my OG collectors who believed, supported, and loved my work always. 

Wishing you all
A Very Happy New Year. 2022
